{
  "stem": "14897.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I had immediately a sort of a job, of sorts, and-- and knew the-- the officers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father said to me-- there were rumors right away that that particular location, where we were, which was near the city of [?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Magdeburg-- ?] some small town I don't remember the name of-- that that part of was really negotiated to go over to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was eventually exchanged and became part of East Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think the River Elbe was-- was the border, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- my father said to me, let's try, as soon as we can, to go west.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't want to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father realized, very astutely, that Poland was likely to fall under the influence of the-- of the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, let's try to go west and get out of here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I think I-- I did this work for approximately maybe three weeks or so.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at around May 7, just a day or two before V-E Day-- that's the end of the war in Europe-- there was a train available for French people to be repatriated to France.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I asked Captain [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Holland, ?] I remember, who was in charge of whatever then, to give me a pass to go to France.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I, my father, and 12 other people, none of whom could speak French, got on this train, which happened to be a cattle train, and we went west.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All the other people were French-- they were women, French women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the majority, I think, were young men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were French prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No borders-- we just went west.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We went through Belgium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went to France.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
